# WAF Targets Configuration for GoTestWAF Testing
# =============================================================================
# Format: name,url,graphql_url,grpc_port
# 
# - name: Identifier for the WAF (used in reports)
# - url: Base URL of the application behind the WAF
# - graphql_url: GraphQL endpoint URL (leave empty if not available)
# - grpc_port: gRPC port (leave empty if not available)
#
# Lines starting with # are comments
# =============================================================================

