# =============================================================================
# Testing Scenarios
# =============================================================================
# 
# 1. Direct (No WAF) - Baseline
#    Test against the echo server directly to establish baseline behavior
#
# 2. Single WAF
#    Place WAF in front of echo server, test through WAF
#
# 3. Multiple WAFs
#    Compare detection rates across different WAF solutions
#
# Architecture for testing:
#
#   ┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐
#   │  GoTestWAF  │────▶│     WAF     │────▶│   Echo Server   │
#   └─────────────┘     └─────────────┘     └─────────────────┘
#                              │
#                    Blocks malicious requests
#                    Allows legitimate requests
#
# =============================================================================
